Package model.cells

Class Summary
BlankCell A BlankCell is a Cell that a Player can pass always.
BreakableWall A BreakableWall is a Wall where a Player can't pass until it's leftTries is equal to zero.
Cell  
Coin A Coin is a Collectable Cell that adds points only the first time it's collected, then it turns it's state to NOTVISIBLE
Collectable  
Destiny Represents the Cell where the Player needs to reach in order to win
Door A Door is a Cell which a Player can pass only when an associated Key was found, and its open.
Key A Key is a Cell which has an associated Door, so when a Player is over it, the door opens.
Transporter A Transporter is a Cell which has a destiny, where the Player will end if it goes through it
Wall A Wall is a Cell which a Player can't Pass
